    </button>
    <div class="faq-a" id="mistake-5-outdated-schema-types"><div class="faq-a-inner"><p>Schema.org evolves continuously. Using deprecated types or properties reduces validity. The <code>MedicalWebPage</code> type was replaced by more specific health types. Some properties have been superseded by newer alternatives.</p></div></div>
